607
00:33:16,587 --> 00:33:18,039
Yeah, thanks.

608
00:33:18,126 --> 00:33:20,666
Well, I'll see you.

609
00:33:23,532 --> 00:33:26,004
Hi. I heard you were awake.

610
00:33:26,596 --> 00:33:28,897
Apparently, without a spleen,
