first thing in the morning.

674
00:37:38,022 --> 00:37:39,633
I just...

675
00:37:41,336 --> 00:37:42,903
I had to see you.

676
00:37:44,567 --> 00:37:46,435
And see the girls.

677
00:37:46,744 --> 00:37:48,779
Life is...

678
00:37:49,759 --> 00:37:51,193
